::Epyon::

He looked over the holo projection.
"Hmmm. Looks good, and I think that other ship would be better command
center, yesss."
He opens a comm link to Wizard.
"Wizard, I need you to start the evacuation of the StarJumper, and start
to take it apart. We are almost ready to go with the City plan. So start
taring it down and getting the parts to the CF."

::Hot Rod::

He slipped away from Prowl and Epyon. He also opened a comm.
"Feline, its Hot Rod again. I think we really need to talk, and patch
things up."

::DrillBit::

"Well RamJet, I dont have a problem with this. The Pack will except this
alliance."
He turned to DarkFate.
"How about your group?"

::Demolition::

He rather enjoyed the show down between Megaton and Depth Charge.

::Dollon::

He got up and put a hand on DarkMouse's shoulder.
"I'm going to get something to eat. You want to come?"

OOC: Ok, where and what is Angel Prime doing? I wasn't really paying
attention to him. But now that he is mine for a month, I kinda need to
know.
